{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-01644/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-01644"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:16:44"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man smiles as a woman eats."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-01644","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-01644"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1/7782ed8c-8df8-4d21-b259-4bc229c3af2f","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:47:47.679Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>In addition to Alma’s red dress in <em>Phantom Thread</em>, similar dresses are also worn by Lena in <em>Punch-Drunk Love</em> and Alana in <em>Licorice Pizza</em>—PTA’s trio of unusual, occasionally twisted romantic comedies.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1179.8472429210133,343.9716840536512,649.4932935916543,689.1058122205663"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1/446a2886-2797-439f-bd9d-c64635150695","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-01T14:48:03.659Z","creator":"Clara Smith","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma’s red dress matches the tablecloths and napkins at the restaurant. Food is very often associated with sexuality and desire in the film, so this similarity represents Reynolds’s hunger for her. She has become part of his “meal,” so to speak. However, this similarity also strips her of her personhood to some degree. She becomes part of the objects on the table, a prop in his life, rather than someone with her own agency and power.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-01644/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:8.114754098360663,754.6609538002979,1157.6937406855438,289.9515648286141"}}}]}]}]}